{
  "texts": [
    "He et al. (2021) suggested that not all generated tokens need to be retrieved.",
    "Instead, a lightweight neural network can be trained to aid the KNN-LM in adaptive retrieval.",
    "Additionally, efficiency can be improved through database streamlining and dimension reduction.",
    "Alon et al. (2022) proposed RETOMATON, an unsupervised, weighted finite automaton built on top of the data store.",
    "RETOMATON is based on saving pointers between successive data store entries and clustering techniques."
  ]
}